
   
    BLACK_MAGIC : MODULE :

        Instead of use ES6 modules we will create 
        a comment like:

    
        //:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::://
        //:                                              ://
        //:            [BLACK_MAGIC:HOTEL13]             ://
        //:                                              ://
        //:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::://

        When the server serves itself , it also 
        injects the source code of[  HOTEL13.JS ]
        by using a simple:

        i_cof.replaceAll( 

            "[BLACK_MAGIC:HOTEL13]" 

        ,   contents_of_file_hotel13_js
        );;

